parts: This document discusses your rights regarding credit card purchases, specifically when you are dissatisfied with goods or services and have tried to resolve the issue with the merchant. It outlines the conditions under which you may have the right to not pay the remaining amount due on the purchase. It also mentions an address for inquiries or disputes.
